<reference id="api_enablelocalaudio">
    <title><ph keyref="enableLocalAudio"/></title>
    <shortdesc id="short"><ph id="shortdesc">Disables/Re-enables the local audio function.</ph></shortdesc>
    <prolog>
        <metadata>
   <keywords>
       <indexterm keyref="enableLocalAudio" />
   </keywords>
        </metadata>
    </prolog>
    <refbody><section id="prototype">
        
        <p conref="../conref/conref_rtc_api.dita#apidef/enableLocalAudio"/>
        </section>
        <section id="detailed_desc">
   
   <p>The audio function is enabled by default. This method disables or re-enables the local audio function, that is, to stop or restart local audio capturing.</p>
   <p>该方法不影响接收或播放远端音频流，<xref keyref="enableLocalAudio"></xref>(<ph keyref="false"/>) 适用于只听不发的用户场景。</p>
   <p>语音功能关闭或重新开启后，会收到回调 <xref keyref="onLocalAudioStateChanged"/>，并报告 <apiname
                    keyref="LOCAL_AUDIO_STREAM_STATE_STOPPED"/>(0) 或 <apiname
                    keyref="LOCAL_AUDIO_STREAM_STATE_RECORDING"/>(1)。</p>
   <note outputclass="note"><ul>
       <li>该方法与 <xref keyref="muteLocalAudioStream"/> 的区别在于：<ul>
                            <li><apiname keyref="enableLocalVideo"/>: 开启或关闭本地语音采集及处理。 If you disable or re-<codeph>enable</codeph> local audio capturing using the `<codeph>enableLocalAudio</codeph>` method, the local user may hear a pause in the remote audio playback.</li>
                            <li><apiname keyref="muteLocalAudioStream"/>: 停止或继续发送本地音频流。</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>       
       <li>You can call this method either before or after joining a channel.</li> 
   </ul></note>
        </section>
        <section id="parameters"><title>Parameter</title>
   <parml>
       <plentry>
  <pt>enabled</pt>
  <pd><ul>
      <li><ph keyref="true"/>true: (Default) Re-enable the local audio function, that is, to start the local audio capturing device (for example, the microphone).</li>
      <li><ph keyref="false"/>false: Disable the local audio function, that is, to stop local audio capturing.</li>
  </ul>     
  </pd>
       </plentry>
   </parml>
        </section>
        <section id="return_values">
   <title>Returns</title>
   <ul>
       <li>0: Success.</li>
       <li>&lt; 0: Failure.</li>
   </ul>
        </section></refbody>
